00:00:13.300 --> 00:00:17.200 align:middle line:10%
>> I do believe that we all have
guides, we all have guardians,

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:20.020 align:middle line:10%
we all have angels,
ancestors who are around you,

00:00:20.020 --> 00:00:21.940 align:middle line:10%
spirit ancestors.

00:00:21.940 --> 00:00:26.860 align:middle line:84%
And it's important that we
ask, that we knock on that door

00:00:26.860 --> 00:00:31.630 align:middle line:84%
