unifies religion, science,

00:32:11.430 --> 00:32:14.280 align:middle line:84%
spirituality in a way that we
can make sense of the world

00:32:14.280 --> 00:32:16.290 align:middle line:90%
with one worldview.

00:32:16.290 --> 00:32:20.340 align:middle line:84%
This panentheism notion
that we're all in this

00:32:20.340 --> 00:32:22.500 align:middle line:84%
together, that there
is an evolution to it,

00:32:22.500 --> 00:32:25.110 align:middle line:84%
that we have free will,
that we contribute

00:32:25.110 --> 00:32:29.920 align:middle line:84%
basically to the evolution
of consciousness itself.

00:32:29.920 --> 00:32:33.450 align:middle line:90%
>> We are a divine masterwork.

00:32:33.450 --> 00:32:36.570 align:middle line:90%
We are the divine masterwork.

00:32:36.570 --> 00:32:40.230 align:middle line:84%
