spiritual beings having

00:32:40.230 --> 00:32:43.980 align:middle line:84%
this little physical experience,
this little mortal experience,

00:32:43.980 --> 00:32:45.330 align:middle line:90%
just to learn--

00:32:45.330 --> 00:32:48.840 align:middle line:84%
again, in a classroom,
not a courtroom-- so

00:32:48.840 --> 00:32:51.420 align:middle line:90%
that we can grow and get better.

00:32:51.420 --> 00:32:52.900 align:middle line:90%
We are the test.

00:32:52.900 --> 00:32:54.100 align:middle line:90%
We are the gathering.

00:32:54.100 --> 00:32:57.640 align:middle line:84%
We are the gathering of all
the DNA from all the cosmos.

00:32:57.640 --> 00:32:59.590 align:middle line:90%
And we're put in one here.

00:32:59.590 --> 00:33:03.270 align:middle line:84%
And that's how we are built
in the image of our creator.

00:33:03.270 --> 00:33:06.660 align:middle line:84%
>> The essence of who we
are is our consciousness.

00:33:06.660 --> 00:33:09.600 align:middle line:84%
People sometimes
compare it with when

00:33:09.600 --> 00:33:13.050 align:middle line:84%
you look through a film,
a projection, what you see

00:33:13.050 --> 00:33:16.230 align:middle line:90%
on the screen is just images.

00:33:16.230 --> 00:33:19.110 align:middle line:84%
It's the same as your
thoughts, but you

00:33:19.110 --> 00:33:22.830 align:middle line:84%
