you just see the light.

00:33:22.830 --> 00:33:26.760 align:middle line:84%
So there's something behind all
your thoughts and your feelings,

00:33:26.760 --> 00:33:31.880 align:middle line:84%
and that's your consciousness,
which is eternal.

00:33:31.880 --> 00:33:35.360 align:middle line:84%
>> I would say that we are
consciousness in the process

00:33:35.360 --> 00:33:36.580 align:middle line:90%
of evolution.

00:33:36.580 --> 00:33:39.410 align:middle line:84%
It's this beautiful
dance of sentient beings

00:33:39.410 --> 00:33:42.350 align:middle line:84%
who are sharing that one
mind, but each manifesting

00:33:42.350 --> 00:33:43.880 align:middle line:90%
is a different perspective.

00:33:43.880 --> 00:33:46.860 align:middle line:84%
I like to look at us as facets
on the edge of a diamond.

00:33:46.860 --> 00:33:49.650 align:middle line:84%
The diamond is the one
mind, that God mind.

00:33:49.650 --> 00:33:51.800 align:middle line:84%
And yet the facets are
each and every one of us

00:33:51.800 --> 00:33:53.580 align:middle line:90%
as an individual perspective.

00:33:53.580 --> 00:33:56.360 align:middle line:84%
And it's how those facets
interact with each other

00:33:56.360 --> 00:34:00.060 align:middle line:84%
that we can help that one mind
in its process of evolution.

00:34:00.060 --> 00:34:05.630 align:middle line:84%
So just as the entrance to the
temple at the Oracle of Delphi,

00:34:05.630 --> 00:34:08.770 align:middle line:84%
there's an inscription
that says, know thyself.

00:34:08.770 --> 00:34:11.989 align:middle line:84%
Well, in fact, I think that's
exactly what the challenge is,

00:34:11.989 --> 00:34:13.139 align:middle line:90%
to know thyself.

00:34:13.139 --> 00:34:16.429 align:middle line:84%
But as you come to recognize,
as the modern science

00:34:16.429 --> 00:34:18.409 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness is
pointing out to us,

00:34:18.409 --> 00:34:21.139 align:middle line:84%
that we're really part of
the mind of the universe.

00:34:21.139 --> 00:34:24.080 align:middle line:84%
That is what is
doing the evolving.

00:34:24.080 --> 00:34:27.440 align:middle line:84%
So it's nothing more than
individual sentient beings

00:34:27.440 --> 00:34:30.840 align:middle line:84%
going through this process
of learning who they are,

00:34:30.840 --> 00:34:34.350 align:middle line:84%
why they're here, and
where this is all going.

00:34:34.350 --> 00:34:36.040 align:middle line:90%
>> God plants us down here.

00:34:36.040 --> 00:34:37.920 align:middle line:90%
We choose to come down.

00:34:37.920 --> 00:34:39.090 align:middle line:90%
We want to grow.

00:34:39.090 --> 00:34:40.929 align:middle line:90%
We want to expand.

00:34:40.929 --> 00:34:42.960 align:middle line:90%
We want to experience.

00:34:42.960 --> 00:34:44.969 align:middle line:84%
Maybe when we get
far enough grown,

00:34:44.969 --> 00:34:48.300 align:middle line:84%
we get to stay home and not
have to come down anymore.

00:34:48.300 --> 00:34:50.909 align:middle line:84%
I don't know the
bigger picture, but I'm

00:34:50.909 --> 00:34:53.610 align:middle line:84%
glad that I strongly believe
that there is a God that's

00:34:53.610 --> 00:34:55.230 align:middle line:90%
controlling the whole thing.

00:34:55.230 --> 00:34:57.990 align:middle line:90%
And I trust him.

00:34:57.990 --> 00:34:59.650 align:middle line:90%
>> So this was the message.

00:34:59.650 --> 00:35:03.060 align:middle line:84%
God said, such folly to
think anything escapes

00:35:03.060 --> 00:35:07.290 align:middle line:84%
my knowing, as when you
were with me all at once all

00:35:07.290 --> 00:35:09.540 align:middle line:84%
that I allowed you
to know, you knew.

00:35:09.540 --> 00:35:12.490 align:middle line:10%
No words were spoken,
nor were they shouted.

00:35:12.490 --> 00:35:15.090 align:middle line:10%
I whispered them to your spirit.

00:35:15.090 --> 00:35:17.440 align:middle line:84%
I discreetly filled
you with knowing.

00:35:17.440 --> 00:35:21.630 align:middle line:84%
Knowing flowed into you as
effortlessly as taking a breath.

00:35:21.630 --> 00:35:23.400 align:middle line:90%
Is it not so?

00:35:23.400 --> 00:35:26.730 align:middle line:84%
No truer words have ever
been spoken or written.

00:35:26.730 --> 00:35:29.230 align:middle line:90%
The great I am is in your core.

00:35:29.230 --> 00:35:31.510 align:middle line:90%
The great I am is the light.

00:35:31.510 --> 00:35:34.860 align:middle line:84%
Even when I am
hidden, still, I am.

00:35:34.860 --> 00:35:39.370 align:middle line:84%
As my energy charged sending me
over each synapse in your brain,

00:35:39.370 --> 00:35:42.630 align:middle line:84%
even those small
fibers knew that I am.

00:35:42.630 --> 00:35:46.050 align:middle line:84%
They rose and fell to
the rhythm I created,

00:35:46.050 --> 00:35:49.590 align:middle line:84%
to the symphony I
composed, I conducted.

00:35:49.590 --> 00:35:52.450 align:middle line:84%
I consider it a tragic
comedy of arrogance

00:35:52.450 --> 00:35:55.950 align:middle line:84%
when man denies what the
smallest innovation knows.

00:35:55.950 --> 00:35:59.820 align:middle line:84%
Man thinks he acts and
moves outside my knowledge.

00:35:59.820 --> 00:36:01.380 align:middle line:90%
How could it be so?

00:36:01.380 --> 00:36:04.230 align:middle line:90%
I say, I proclaim he does not.

00:36:04.230 --> 00:36:08.430 align:middle line:84%
His own fibers clutch
themselves laughing at the idea.

00:36:08.430 --> 00:36:12.960 align:middle line:84%
I am the flower, the wind, the
rain, the sinew, the marrow,

00:36:12.960 --> 00:36:17.700 align:middle line:84%
the rock, the author, the maker,
the touch that set in motion

00:36:17.700 --> 00:36:20.332 align:middle line:84%
all that you see,
all that you know,

00:36:20.332 --> 00:36:23.010 align:middle line:84%
and all that you
do not see or know.

00:36:23.010 --> 00:36:24.550 align:middle line:90%
I knit you.

00:36:24.550 --> 00:36:26.110 align:middle line:90%
I put breath in you.

00:36:26.110 --> 00:36:28.770 align:middle line:90%
I am coded in every cell.

00:36:28.770 --> 00:36:33.690 align:middle line:84%
Each nanosecond of time falls
in step as I will it so.

00:36:33.690 --> 00:36:34.740 align:middle line:90%
I am in you.

00:36:34.740 --> 00:36:36.030 align:middle line:90%
I am all.

00:36:36.030 --> 00:36:39.990 align:middle line:84%
Even when you perceive
nothing, still, I am there.

00:36:39.990 --> 00:36:42.990 align:middle line:84%
As I tell you this here
and now, pressing my truth

00:36:42.990 --> 00:36:46.320 align:middle line:84%
into your breast, your very
heart presses it further in.

